name: Reveries
description: I only see love. Nothing else. I stare at love. I'll be staring here forever. Stuck on the O, I'm complete. I've got everything. Gone. I don't even know why. Love made me so happy. I still see its contours, I would like to distinguish them better but they always become more indistinct, shadows dancing in front of me. Little by little they disappear as time goes by. But one day, suddenly, they will come back for a moment. Reveries.
